1. *Šolja* kafe mi je najvažnija stvar ujutru. (The *cup* of coffee is the most important thing for me in the morning.)
2. Stavila sam *šolju* na sto i sipala vodu. (I put the *cup* on the table and poured water.)
3. Kada je završila sa kafom, oprala je *šolju* sapunicom. (After finishing her coffee, she washed the *cup* with soap.)
4. Molim vas da mi donesete još jednu *šolju* kafe. (Please bring me another *cup* of coffee.)
5. Mama mi je kupila novu *šolju* za rođendan. (My mom bought me a new *cup* for my birthday.)
6. Uspela sam da slomim samo jednu *šolju* iz celog seta. (I only managed to break one *cup* from the whole set.)
7. *Šolja* se brzo ohladila pa sam morao da zagrejem kafu u mikrotalasnoj. (The *cup* cooled down quickly so I had to heat up the coffee in the microwave.)
8. Zamolio sam je da mi pozajmi jednu *šolju* jer sam zaboravio svoju kod kuće. (I asked her to lend me a *cup* because I forgot mine at home.)
9. Ona drži *šolju* čvrsto dok pije čaj. (She holds the *cup* tightly while drinking tea.)
10. Moram da pazim na svoju *šolju* jer mi je jako draga. (I have to take care of my *cup* because it is very dear to me.)